Sentencas: Effects of a sintering agent for La-doped ceria (LDC) as a buffer layer to prevent a chemical reaction between Ni in anode and Sr- and Mg-doped lanthanum gallate (LSGM) electrolyte during sintering were studied for improving sintering and electrical properties.
Titulo: Improved sintering and electrical properties of La-doped CeO2 buffer layer for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells using doped LaGaO3 film prepared by screen printing process
